name: FOLLOW-007
description:
Welcome to the 'FOLLOW' Series

In every phase of life, we're following something or someone, but does that mean they're ahead of us? I hate to break it to you but we're in an endless loop. Who you follow, prolly following someone too! Oh, wait, are you taking the lead?

--------------------

Collecting this and other works by Jakestudyos means supporting a dream of the artist to continue his craft while making a living.
Join Jakestudyos on his journey and evolution.
